  # Get Pareto Curve by ID

  Returns a single Pareto curve definition.

  ## Path Parameters

  | Param | Description |
  |-------|-------------|
  | id | Pareto curve identifier (e.g., `pareto-001`, `pareto-002`, `pareto-003`) |

  ## Response Shape

  ```json
  {
    "id": "pareto-001",
    "submissionId": "sub-001",
    "systemId": "system1",
    "description": "System 1 - DeepSeek R1 Pareto frontier",
    "minConcurrency": 1,
    "maxConcurrency": 64
  }
  ```

  ## Related Endpoints

  To get the data points for this curve, use:
  `GET /api/dataPoints?paretoCurveId=pareto-001`
}
